      <h1>Account of Bills of Exchange Drawn on<br/>John Adams and Henry Laurens</h1>
      <div class="docbody">
        <div class="opener">
          <table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">Paris June 22<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">d.</span> 1784<a class="ptr" href="#ADMS-06-16-02-0146-fn-0001" id="ADMS-06-16-02-0146-fn-0001-ptr">1</a></td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
        </div>
        <p style="text-indent: 1.5em; text-align: left;">Account of Bills of Exchange drawn by the Comm<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">rs.</span> of Loans in America on Henry Laurence &amp; John Adams Esq<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">rs.</span> at Amsterdam.</p>
        <table class="bodytext"> 
          <tr>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">1780</td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre;">Feb<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">y.</span> 25</td>
	      <td colspan="2">In whose favor Charles Harady N<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">o.</span> 5 . . . . 1100 . . . . . . . . </td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre;">1.100</td>
	    </tr>
          <tr>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;"></td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre;">July6<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">th.</span></td>
	      <td>Joseph Carlton from T Smith 137 Bills of 550 Guilders N<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">o.</span> 32 @ 41 44 @ 61 65 @ 75 77 @ 79 82 &amp; 83 86 @ 103 105 @ 139 144 @ 152 167 @ 190 192 &amp; 193 . . . . . say 132 @ 550 <br/>Ditto Bills of 824 Guilders 53. N<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">o.</span> 31 @ 83 . . . . . Bills of 1100 28. N<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">o.</span> 27 @ 54</td>
	      <td class="brace"><img src="images/brace-close-trans.png" alt="}" class="brace" style="height: 6.5em; width: 21px;"/></td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre; vertical-align: middle;">147.072</td>
	    </tr>
          <tr>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;"></td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre;">Oct<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">r.</span> 26<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">th.</span></td>
	      <td>Nat Tracy 1 @ 22 is 22 Bills of 2494 1 @ 44 is 44 @ 1248 . . .</td>
	      <td class="brace"><img src="images/brace-close-trans.png" alt="}" class="brace" style="height: 1.5em; width: 12px;"/></td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre; vertical-align: middle;">109.780</td>
