	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
          <tr>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;"></td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre;">Jan<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">y</span> 27</td>
	      <td>Tho<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">s.</span> Lee &amp; J. C. Jones 1 @ 100 is 100 of 550 1 @ 112 is 112 @ 1100 1 of 142 2/3 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</td>
	      <td class="brace"><img src="images/brace-close-trans.png" alt="}" class="brace" style="height: 2em; width: 14px;"/></td>
	      <td style="white-space: pre; vertical-align: middle;">178.342 2/3</td>
	    </tr>
